  <summary date="2022-04-12T16:44:37Z" status="Introduced in House">Nullify Occupational Safety and Health Administration Act or the NOSHA Act

This bill abolishes the Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA). OSHA, which is part of the Department of Labor, sets and enforces workplace safety and health standards and provides related training, outreach, education, and assistance.</summary>
